00:38:00.101 --> 00:38:01.160
We all have in this room.

00:38:01.160 --> 00:38:02.020
We've all had it.

00:38:02.020 --> 00:38:03.620
We all will continue to have it.

00:38:03.620 --> 00:38:06.950
The only thing we can control
is our internal resilience.

00:38:06.950 --> 00:38:09.600
And we can build
that resilience up so

00:38:09.600 --> 00:38:13.530
that we are more capable of
dealing with those situations

00:38:13.530 --> 00:38:16.150
without being so
torn up by them.

00:38:16.150 --> 00:38:17.256
So that's my point there.

