00:41:21.830 --> 00:41:25.790
inclusive, and have more
psychological safety

00:41:25.790 --> 00:41:27.860
and trust with each
other as also governing

00:41:27.860 --> 00:41:31.822
factors of success, not
just who's at the top?

00:41:31.822 --> 00:41:33.780
EMMA SEPPALA: Well, that's
one of the reasons I

00:41:33.780 --> 00:41:35.040
wrote this book.

00:41:35.040 --> 00:41:38.220
It's categorized in the
