00:41:44.150 --> 00:41:47.050
And by impacting and benefiting
the entire organization,

00:41:47.050 --> 00:41:49.540
they also benefit all of
those employees' families.

00:41:49.540 --> 00:41:51.910
I mean, it's a
huge repercussion.

00:41:51.910 --> 00:41:54.270
And really what I would
say is, look at the data.

00:41:54.270 --> 00:41:58.880
There is so much data now that
shows that having a bad boss

00:41:58.880 --> 00:42:02.390
is bad for your heart, like
