00:42:02.390 --> 00:42:06.670
It leads to higher
inflammation, literally.

00:42:06.670 --> 00:42:07.510
This is dramatic.

00:42:07.510 --> 00:42:10.260
And yet, people
don't know about it.

00:42:10.260 --> 00:42:11.460
And the opposite is true.

00:42:11.460 --> 00:42:13.470
So if you have a
organization that's

00:42:13.470 --> 00:42:17.595
supported by trust,
respect, empathy, it

00:42:17.595 --> 00:42:18.970
doesn't mean you
have to be soft.

00:42:18.970 --> 00:42:20.720
It doesn't mean you
